{"tid":2447828,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"威廉三子女炮製心意卡向「戴安娜嫲嫲」致意 夏洛特：「爸爸很想念你」","createTime":"2021-03-15T12:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T13:38:28.000Z","uid":17387,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"75107a1ccccf4b91fa6bc872f0cc31ce7f4d747a","tid":2447828,"uid":17387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:52:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jOjMBwrgC1--OHsRMoC3lBr226s=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MA72EBHYRZBKVNQ73OEYRQPBHE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjOjMBwrgC1--OHsRMoC3lBr226s%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMA72EBHYRZBKVNQ73OEYRQPBHE.jpg&h=60366c98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周日（3月14日）是英國母親節，英國威廉王子三個子女動手製作心意卡向「戴安娜嫲嫲」致意，還寫道「爸爸很想念你」。早前因接受美國名嘴奧花雲費專訪而引起軒然大波的哈里王子，則表示會派人到亡母、已故威爾斯王妃戴安娜的墓地獻花。<br />\n<br />\n威廉王子及妻子凱蒂的官方Twitter上載了由喬治王子、夏洛特公主及路易王子製作的心意卡，形容今年再一次因疫情導致家人分隔兩地，不少人都期盼在不久的將來，能夠為他們的母親送上擁抱。<br />\n<br />\n喬治及夏洛特皆稱呼威廉王子母親戴妃為「戴安娜嫲嫲」，內容說他們都很愛嫲嫲和經常想到她，夏洛特更說「爸爸很想念你」，年紀最小的路易手畫了一張有大心心的卡，以及貼上一些動物貼紙。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-ZQ79paRqnC3Bu7l0mDevN3HDfc=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JMVWW7HEPNDUHJO2TEJXTDUGCM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-ZQ79paRqnC3Bu7l0mDevN3HDfc%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJMVWW7HEPNDUHJO2TEJXTDUGCM.jpg&h=799eee50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其Twitter後來再發佈多一則帖子，是喬治、夏洛特及路易一起製作的蛋糕，相中可見這個蛋糕滿佈忌廉和糖霜，頂部亦有一些心型裝飾，帖文亦發佈了凱蒂小時候跟母親卡蘿爾（Carole Middleton）的合照<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/B_ek8G0XrlxnG0nVJaNIypZhrK0=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EIOTNAJRRJFTBOA3FJAEJIW6AM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FB_ek8G0XrlxnG0nVJaNIypZhrK0%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEIOTNAJRRJFTBOA3FJAEJIW6AM.jpg&h=34884688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n身在美國的哈里王子則透露他會安排送花到戴妃墓地，戴妃的遺體被安葬在奧爾索普莊園（Althorp）。<span class=\"red\">哈里王子在奧花雲費的專訪，曾提及如果戴妃仍然在生，看到他和梅根離開皇室會感到傷心，並會對事情的發展感到憤怒。</span><br />\n<br />\n仆街仔哈里又借老母過橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe12ebadfb12cb339d05705c126a91e4e60e0cf","tid":2447828,"uid":19012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:54:02.000Z","msg":"夏洛特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個樣"},{"pid":"09c23abc846d396636d25171c07d9612d36b5ddc","tid":2447828,"uid":210669,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:56:53.000Z","msg":"夏洛特好似事頭婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2515c1da2ccf33fcf81de4af90dbb61ea13b7ae7","tid":2447828,"uid":35702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfe12ebadfb12cb339d05705c126a91e4e60e0cf","tid":2447828,"uid":19012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:54:02.000Z","msg":"夏洛特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:58:26.000Z","msg":"如果佢光頭就會變到同老豆一樣樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28718dbcb2e1b9d2859113c7a53d7d6e6063bc21","tid":2447828,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09c23abc846d396636d25171c07d9612d36b5ddc","tid":2447828,